    "Background": {
      "text": "Caused by\nvaricella zoster virus\ncausing varicella (chicken pox) and later zoster (\nShingles\n)\nContagious until last lesion crusts over\nFluid from open vesicles contains live virus\n[1]\nIncubation period is 10-21 days with symptoms starting around day 14\n[1]",
